{
  "title": "ds-interactivity - core option matrix (light)",
  "description": "Combined test bench for the 5 interactivity skills that share an absolute layout: ds-tokens, ds-inputs, ds-defaults, ds-drilldowns, ds-visibility. Each section tests one skill. Tabs have their own dashboard because tabbed layout cannot coexist with absolute layout. SPL is makeresults-based so this runs anywhere.",
  "theme": "light",
  "defaults": {
    "dataSources": {
      "ds.search": {
        "options": {
          "queryParameters": {
            "earliest": "$global_time.earliest$",
            "latest": "$global_time.latest$"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "inputs": {
    "input_global_time": {
      "type": "input.timerange",
      "title": "Time range",
      "options": {
        "token": "global_time",
        "defaultValue": "-24h@h,now"
      }
    },
    "input_index": {
      "type": "input.dropdown",
      "title": "Index",
      "options": {
        "token": "selected_index",
        "items": [
          {
            "label": "All",
            "value": "*"
          },
          {
            "label": "auth",
            "value": "auth"
          },
          {
            "label": "web",
            "value": "web"
          },
          {
            "label": "fw",
            "value": "fw"
          }
        ],
        "defaultValue": "*"
      }
    },
    "input_status": {
      "type": "input.multiselect",
      "title": "Status",
      "options": {
        "token": "status",
        "defaultValue": [
          "200",
          "201"
        ],
        "items": [
          {
            "label": "200 OK",
            "value": "200"
          },
          {
            "label": "201 Created",
            "value": "201"
          },
          {
            "label": "404 Not Found",
            "value": "404"
          },
          {
            "label": "500 Error",
            "value": "500"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "input_search_text": {
      "type": "input.text",
      "title": "Search filter",
      "options": {
        "token": "search_text",
        "defaultValue": "*"
      }
    },
    "input_host_dynamic": {
      "type": "input.dropdown",
      "title": "Host (dynamic)",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_hosts"
      },
      "options": {
        "token": "host_filter",
        "defaultValue": "*",
        "items": "> primary | frame(label, value) | prepend(formattedStatics) | objects()"
      },
      "context": {
        "formattedConfig": {
          "number": {
            "prefix": ""
          }
        },
        "formattedStatics": "> statics | formatByType(formattedConfig)",
        "statics": [
          [
            "All"
          ],
          [
            "*"
          ]
        ],
        "label": "> primary | seriesByName(\"label\") | renameSeries(\"label\") | formatByType(formattedConfig)",
        "value": "> primary | seriesByName(\"label\") | renameSeries(\"value\") | formatByType(formattedConfig)"
      }
    }
  },
  "dataSources": {
    "ds_hosts": {
      "type": "ds.test",
      "options": {
        "data": {
          "fields": [
            {
              "name": "label"
            },
            {
              "name": "value"
            }
          ],
          "columns": [
            [
              "web-01",
              "web-02",
              "web-03"
            ],
            [
              "web-01",
              "web-02",
              "web-03"
            ]
          ]
        }
      }
    },
    "ds_token_demo": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| makeresults | eval msg=\"index=$selected_index$ status=$status$ filter=$search_text$ host=$host_filter$ time=$global_time.earliest$..$global_time.latest$\" | table msg"
      }
    },
    "ds_table_rows": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| makeresults count=5 | streamstats count AS row | eval host=case(row=1,\"web-01\",row=2,\"web-02\",row=3,\"db-01\",row=4,\"app-01\",row=5,\"cache-01\"), action=case(row%2=0,\"allow\",1=1,\"deny\"), bytes=row*1024 | table host action bytes"
      }
    },
    "ds_selected_detail": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| makeresults | eval host=\"$selected_host$\", note=\"clicked from upstream table\" | table host note"
      }
    },
    "ds_count_kpi": {
      "type": "ds.search",
      "options": {
        "query": "| makeresults | eval count=42 | table count"
      }
    }
  },
  "visualizations": {
    "viz_section_intro": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "# `ds-interactivity` core matrix\n\nOne dashboard, five interactivity skills. Each section is owned by one SKILL.md.\n\n- \u00a71 **ds-tokens** \u2014 token output panel\n- \u00a72 **ds-inputs** \u2014 input flavours (timerange, dropdown, multiselect, text, dynamic dropdown)\n- \u00a73 **ds-defaults** \u2014 global time wiring\n- \u00a74 **ds-drilldowns** \u2014 setToken / linkToDashboard / linkToSearch / customUrl\n- \u00a75 **ds-visibility** \u2014 show / hide based on token state",
        "fontSize": "small"
      }
    },
    "viz_section1_header": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## \u00a71 ds-tokens\n\nThe panel below shows every token resolved end-to-end. Change any input above and watch the string update.",
        "fontSize": "small"
      }
    },
    "viz_token_echo": {
      "type": "splunk.singlevalue",
      "title": "Token echo",
      "description": "Shows that $selected_index$, $status$, $search_text$, $host_filter$, and $global_time.earliest$ / $global_time.latest$ all resolve correctly.",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_token_demo"
      },
      "options": {
        "majorValue": "> primary | seriesByName(\"msg\") | lastPoint()",
        "majorFontSize": 14,
        "shouldUseThousandSeparators": false
      }
    },
    "viz_section2_header": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## \u00a72 ds-inputs\n\n5 input flavours wired above:\n- `input.timerange` \u2014 `global_time` (with `.earliest` / `.latest` accessors)\n- `input.dropdown` \u2014 `selected_index`\n- `input.multiselect` \u2014 `status` (array, comma-joined in token expansion)\n- `input.text` \u2014 `search_text`\n- `input.dropdown` w/ DOS items \u2014 `host_filter` (populated from `ds_hosts`)",
        "fontSize": "small"
      }
    },
    "viz_inputs_proof": {
      "type": "splunk.table",
      "title": "Inputs \u2192 tokens (live)",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_token_demo"
      },
      "options": {
        "showInternalFields": false
      }
    },
    "viz_section3_header": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## \u00a73 ds-defaults\n\nThe `defaults.dataSources.\"ds.search\".options.queryParameters` block wires `$global_time.earliest$` / `$global_time.latest$` into every search above. None of the `ds.search` entries set their own `queryParameters` \u2014 the default flows through.",
        "fontSize": "small"
      }
    },
    "viz_kpi_default_time": {
      "type": "splunk.singlevalue",
      "title": "KPI driven by defaults",
      "description": "This `ds.search` declares no queryParameters. The dashboard-level defaults block wires global_time into it.",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_count_kpi"
      },
      "options": {
        "majorValue": "> primary | seriesByName(\"count\") | lastPoint()",
        "underLabel": "events (default time wired)"
      }
    },
    "viz_section4_header": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## \u00a74 ds-drilldowns\n\nClick a row in the table below.\n\n- **setToken** \u2014 captures `row.host.value` into `$selected_host$`. The detail panel in \u00a75 shows it.\n- **linkToSearch** \u2014 opens the Splunk search UI prefilled with `index=main host=<row>`.\n- **linkToDashboard** \u2014 navigates to `host_detail_view` (placeholder app=`search`, dashboard=`host_detail_view`).\n- **customUrl** \u2014 opens an external investigation URL with URL-encoded row values.",
        "fontSize": "small"
      }
    },
    "viz_drilldown_table": {
      "type": "splunk.table",
      "title": "Drilldown source",
      "description": "Click any row to fire all four drilldown actions. setToken populates $selected_host$ for \u00a75.",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_table_rows"
      },
      "options": {
        "drilldown": "all",
        "showInternalFields": false
      },
      "eventHandlers": [
        {
          "type": "drilldown.setToken",
          "options": {
            "tokens": [
              {
                "token": "selected_host",
                "key": "row.host.value"
              },
              {
                "token": "selected_action",
                "key": "row.action.value"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "viz_drilldown_table_url": {
      "type": "splunk.table",
      "title": "Drilldown \u2014 customUrl",
      "description": "Click a row to open an external URL with URL-encoded row values via |u filter.",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_table_rows"
      },
      "options": {
        "drilldown": "all",
        "showInternalFields": false
      },
      "eventHandlers": [
        {
          "type": "drilldown.customUrl",
          "options": {
            "url": "https://example.com/investigate?host=$row.host.value|u$&action=$row.action.value|u$",
            "newTab": true
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "viz_drilldown_table_search": {
      "type": "splunk.table",
      "title": "Drilldown \u2014 linkToSearch",
      "description": "Opens Splunk Search with a prefilled query and the dashboard's current time range.",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_table_rows"
      },
      "options": {
        "drilldown": "all",
        "showInternalFields": false
      },
      "eventHandlers": [
        {
          "type": "drilldown.linkToSearch",
          "options": {
            "query": "index=main host=$row.host.value$ | stats count by sourcetype",
            "earliest": "$global_time.earliest$",
            "latest": "$global_time.latest$",
            "newTab": true
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "viz_drilldown_table_dash": {
      "type": "splunk.table",
      "title": "Drilldown \u2014 linkToDashboard",
      "description": "Navigates to host_detail_view in the search app, passing form.host and form.earliest as URL params.",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_table_rows"
      },
      "options": {
        "drilldown": "all",
        "showInternalFields": false
      },
      "eventHandlers": [
        {
          "type": "drilldown.linkToDashboard",
          "options": {
            "app": "search",
            "dashboard": "host_detail_view",
            "newTab": true,
            "tokens": {
              "form.host": "$row.host.value$",
              "form.earliest": "$global_time.earliest$"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "viz_section5_header": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## \u00a75 ds-visibility\n\nThree panels below toggle on different token states of `$selected_host$`:\n- **panel A** \u2014 visible only when `$selected_host$` is set (after a row click in \u00a74)\n- **panel B** \u2014 visible only when `$selected_host$` equals `web-01`\n- **panel C** \u2014 visible only when `$selected_host$` is unset (default state)\n\nClick rows in \u00a74 to flip these on and off.",
        "fontSize": "small"
      }
    },
    "viz_visibility_a_set": {
      "type": "splunk.table",
      "title": "A \u2014 visible when $selected_host$ is set",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_selected_detail"
      },
      "options": {
        "showInternalFields": false
      },
      "visibility": "$selected_host$!=\"\""
    },
    "viz_visibility_b_match": {
      "type": "splunk.singlevalue",
      "title": "B \u2014 visible only when host == web-01",
      "dataSources": {
        "primary": "ds_selected_detail"
      },
      "options": {
        "majorValue": "> primary | seriesByName(\"host\") | lastPoint()",
        "underLabel": "matched web-01"
      },
      "visibility": "$selected_host$==\"web-01\""
    },
    "viz_visibility_c_unset": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "_(C \u2014 initial state: no host selected. Click a row in \u00a74 to hide this and reveal A/B.)_",
        "fontSize": "small"
      },
      "visibility": "$selected_host$==\"\""
    }
  },
  "layout": {
    "type": "absolute",
    "options": {
      "width": 1440,
      "height": 2400,
      "backgroundColor": "#FAEAD8"
    },
    "globalInputs": [
      "input_global_time",
      "input_index",
      "input_status",
      "input_search_text",
      "input_host_dynamic"
    ],
    "structure": [
